Build Autotools Build Tree Toolchain Project.
execute the test only when both parameter  test_build_tree_toolchain and build_tree_path are set. Set build_tree_path or  test_build_tree_toolchain to blank to skip this test case.
a) in project explorer, create new c/c++ project using GNU Autotools  Hello World ANSI C Autotools Project template
b) right click on the project, go to configure and select  "Configure/Configure as Yocto Project Autotools project (alpha)" 
c) in prompted project properties select Build Tree toolchain profile -> click "apply and close"
d) refresh project explorer tab  
e) pin "CDT Global Build Consolse"
f) right click on project -> select "Reconfigure Project" -> validate toolchain in console .
g) right click on project -> select "Build Project"-> validate toolchain in console.
